{
  "id": 5090807862394880,
  "name": "Manifest localization",
  "summary": "Supports localization of manifest members so apps can adapt their names, descriptions, icons, and shortcuts to the user’s language and region. Developers provide localized values in the web app manifest, and the browser automatically selects the appropriate resources based on the user’s language settings, introducing language support across different markets.",
