  "tag_review": "TAG review is not necessary because this feature implements behavior that is already fully specified in the Web App Manifest specification (*_localized members), with the architecture and localization model designed and reviewed in W3C (primarily via the Internationalization Working Group). Although Chromium may be an early or first implementation, this work does not introduce new web‑exposed capabilities, new architectural design choices, or new security or privacy properties. Given the lack of remaining architectural design space for TAG feedback to influence, TAG review would not add meaningful additional signal for this feature.",
